<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Street Axis - 专业街舞培训</title>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload', 'data-turbolinks-eval': 'false' %>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #4A4A4A;
            background-color: #FAF8F5;
        }
        
        /* 导航栏 */
        .navbar {
            background-color: rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.1);
            padding: 20px 0;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }
        
        .navbar.scrolled {
            background-color: rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.98);
            padding: 15px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.08);
        }
        
        .nav-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: #8B7355;
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }
        
        .nav-menu {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        .nav-menu li {
            margin-left: 40px;
        }
        
        .nav-menu a {
            color: #6B6B6B;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        .nav-menu a:hover {
            color: #8B7355;
        }
        
        .user-area {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .nav-link {
            color: #6B6B6B;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .nav-link:hover {
            color: #8B7355;
        }
        
        .nav-btn {
            padding: 10px 24px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Georgia', 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
        }
        
        .nav-btn-primary {
            background-color: #8B7355;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            border: 1px solid #8B7355;
        }
        
        .nav-btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #6B5B45;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            border-color: #6B5B45;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        
        .login-btn {
            background-color: #8B7355;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Georgia', 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
        }
        
        .login-btn:hover {
            background-color: #6B5B45;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        
        .user-dropdown {
            position: relative;
            margin-left: 25px;
            display: inline-block;
            z-index: 1001;
        }
        
        .user-avatar {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #8B7355;
            color: #FAF8F5;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 400;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .user-avatar:hover {
            background-color: #6B5B45;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        
        .dropdown-menu {
            position: absolute;
            top: 100%;
            right: 0;
            background-color: #FAF8F5;
            color: #4A4A4A;
            min-width: 200px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.15);
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 8px 0;
            margin-top: 12px;
            visibility: hidden;
            opacity: 0;
            z-index: 9999;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            pointer-events: none;
            border: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.1);
        }
        
        .dropdown-menu.show {
            visibility: visible;
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
            pointer-events: auto;
        }
        
        .user-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.1);
        }
        
        .user-avatar-large {
            width: 52px;
            height: 52px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #8B7355;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #FAF8F5;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-right: 14px;
        }
        
        .user-details {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .user-name {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            color: #4A4A4A;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .user-email {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #8B8B8B;
        }
        
        .menu-divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.1);
            margin: 4px 0;
        }
        
        .dropdown-menu .menu-item {
            display: block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            color: #6B6B6B !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            text-align: left;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .dropdown-menu .menu-item:hover {
            background-color: rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.08);
            color: #8B7355 !important;
        }
        
        .dropdown-menu form {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .logout-btn {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            color: #6B6B6B;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            text-align: left;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .logout-btn:hover {
            background-color: rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.08);
            color: #8B7355;
        }
        
        /* 轮播图 */
        .carousel {
            position: relative;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .carousel-slide {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 1.2s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .carousel-slide.active {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        
        .carousel-slide::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.3) 0%, rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.1) 100%);
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .carousel-slide img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: brightness(0.95) contrast(1.05);
        }
        
        .carousel-content {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            text-align: center;
            color: #FAF8F5;
            z-index: 10;
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 0 40px;
        }
        
        .carousel-content h1 {
            font-size: 56px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        
        .carousel-content p {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        .carousel-btn {
            background-color: #8B7355;
            color: #FAF8F5;
            border: none;
            padding: 16px 48px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 400;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .carousel-btn:hover {
            background-color: #6B5B45;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.3);
        }
        
        .carousel-indicators {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 50px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        
        .indicator {
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.4);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .indicator.active {
            background-color: #FAF8F5;
            transform: scale(1.3);
        }
        
        /* 街舞分类展示区 */
        .categories {
            padding: 120px 40px;
            background-color: #FAF8F5;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
        }
        
        .section-title h2 {
            font-size: 42px;
            color: #4A4A4A;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        
        .section-title p {
            font-size: 17px;
            color: #8B8B8B;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .categories-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
        }
        
        .category-card {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 2px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.08);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.05);
        }
        
        .category-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.15);
        }
        
        .category-image {
            height: 240px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .category-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.6s ease;
            filter: brightness(0.95) contrast(1.05);
        }
        
        .category-card:hover .category-image img {
            transform: scale(1.08);
        }
        
        .category-content {
            padding: 28px;
        }
        
        .category-content h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #4A4A4A;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .category-content p {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #8B8B8B;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        .category-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #8B7355;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 400;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border: 1px solid #8B7355;
        }
        
        .category-btn:hover {
            background-color: #8B7355;
            color: #FAF8F5;
        }
        
        /* 最新活动/课程展示模块 */
        .events {
            padding: 120px 40px;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
        }
        
        .events-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(360px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
        }
        
        .event-card {
            background-color: #FAF8F5;
            border-radius: 2px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.08);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.05);
        }
        
        .event-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.15);
        }
        
        .event-image {
            height: 240px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .event-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.6s ease;
            filter: brightness(0.95) contrast(1.05);
        }
        
        .event-card:hover .event-image img {
            transform: scale(1.08);
        }
        
        .event-content {
            padding: 28px;
        }
        
        .event-date {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #8B7355;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .event-content h3 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #4A4A4A;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .event-content p {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #8B8B8B;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        .event-location {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #9B9B9B;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }
        
        .event-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #8B7355;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 400;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border: 1px solid #8B7355;
        }
        
        .event-btn:hover {
            background-color: #8B7355;
            color: #FAF8F5;
        }
        
        /* 关于我们 */
        .about {
            padding: 120px 40px;
            background-color: #FAF8F5;
        }
        
        .about-content {
            display: flex;
            gap: 60px;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .about-text {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .about-text h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #4A4A4A;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            margin-top: 36px;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .about-text h3:first-child {
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        
        .about-text p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #8B8B8B;
            line-height: 1.9;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        .about-image {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 550px;
        }
        
        .about-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 2px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.12);
            filter: brightness(0.95) contrast(1.05);
        }
        
        /* 页脚 */
        .footer {
            background-color: #4A4A4A;
            color: #FAF8F5;
            padding: 80px 40px 40px;
        }
        
        .footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
            gap: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        
        .footer-column h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #D4C4A8;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .footer-column ul {
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        .footer-column ul li {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .footer-column ul li a {
            color: #C8C8C8;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        .footer-column ul li a:hover {
            color: #D4C4A8;
        }
        
        .footer-column p {
            color: #C8C8C8;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.9;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }
        
        .social-links a {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.12);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #FAF8F5;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .social-links a:hover {
            background-color: #8B7355;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        .footer-bottom {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.1);
            padding-top: 32px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #A8A8A8;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }
        
        /* 响应式设计 */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-menu {
                display: none;
            }
            
            .carousel-content h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
            }
            
            .carousel-content p {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            
            .section-title h2 {
                font-size: 32px;
            }
            
            .categories,
            .events,
            .about {
                padding: 80px 20px;
            }
            
            .about-content {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            .about-image {
                max-width: 100%;
            }
            
            .nav-container {
                padding: 0 20px;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .carousel-content h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            
            .carousel-content p {
                font-size: 15px;
            }
            
            .section-title h2 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            
            .categories-grid,
            .events-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .carousel-btn {
                padding: 14px 36px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 导航栏 -->
    <nav class="navbar" id="navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="<%= root_path %>" class="logo">Street Axis</a>
            
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <li><%= link_to "首页", root_path %></li>
                <li><%= link_to "街舞分类", categories_path %></li>
                <li><%= link_to "最新活动", events_path %></li>
                <li><%= link_to "关于我们", about_path %></li>
                <li><%= link_to "联系我们", contact_path %></li>
            </ul>
            
            <div class="user-area">
                <% if !user_signed_in? %>
                <%= link_to "注册", new_user_registration_path, class: "nav-link" %>
                <%= link_to "登录", new_user_session_path, class: "login-btn" %>
                <% else %>
                <div class="user-dropdown">
                    <div class="user-avatar" id="user-avatar"><%= current_user.email.first.upcase %></div>
                    <div class="dropdown-menu">
                        <div class="user-info">
                            <div class="user-avatar-large"><%= current_user.email.first.upcase %></div>
                            <div class="user-details">
                                <div class="user-name"><%= current_user.email.split('@').first %></div>
                                <div class="user-email"><%= current_user.email %></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="menu-divider"></div>
                        <a href="<%= user_profile_path %>" class="menu-item">个人中心</a>
                        <a href="<%= user_courses_path %>" class="menu-item">我的课程</a>
                        <% if current_user.is_admin? || current_user.role.present? %>
                        <a href="<%= admin_root_path %>" class="menu-item">⚙️ 后台管理</a>
                        <% end %>
                        <div class="menu-divider"></div>
                        <%= form_for(current_user, as: :user, url: destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete) do |f| %>
                            <button type="submit" class="menu-item logout-btn">退出登录</button>
                        <% end %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <% end %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    
    <!-- 轮播图 -->
    <section class="carousel" id="home">
        <div class="carousel-slide active">
            <img src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=hip%20hop%20dancers%20performing%20in%20urban%20setting%2C%20dynamic%20movement%2C%20vibrant%20colors%2C%20professional%20photography&image_size=landscape_16_9" alt="街舞表演">
            <div class="carousel-content">
                <h1>释放你的街舞激情</h1>
                <p>加入我们的街舞社区，展示你的才华，结识志同道合的朋友</p>
                <button class="carousel-btn">立即加入</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="carousel-slide">
            <img src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=breakdancers%20in%20street%20battle%2C%20intense%20competition%2C%20urban%20background%2C%20high%20energy&image_size=landscape_16_9" alt="街舞比赛">
            <div class="carousel-content">
                <h1>参与精彩的街舞比赛</h1>
                <p>展示你的技巧，与顶尖舞者一较高下，赢取丰厚奖励</p>
                <button class="carousel-btn">查看比赛</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="carousel-slide">
            <img src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=hip%20hop%20dance%20class%2C%20professional%20instructor%2C%20students%20learning%2C%20modern%20studio&image_size=landscape_16_9" alt="街舞课程">
            <div class="carousel-content">
                <h1>专业街舞课程</h1>
